{"tid":1646049,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"工聯會調查：近四成半受訪會員擔心未來開工不足或被裁員","createTime":"2019-10-11T06:40:34.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-11T15:10:36.000Z","uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"c3e33068bed86ec7ee9c07838890e4b2875a769d","tid":1646049,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-11T06:40:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://newsstatic.rthk.hk/images/mfile_1485537_1_L_20191011132606.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnewsstatic.rthk.hk%2Fimages%2Fmfile_1485537_1_L_20191011132606.jpg&h=24e5159c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1485537-20191011.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1485537-20191011.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=6p%2BW5B2gHvlBGPj8iPYwcnza4IX%2BHJq2V8VgSm%2B5QfQ%3D&h=c542f3bb\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1485537-20191011.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=2d6a30ba\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1485537-20191011.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a><br />\n<br />\n工聯會調查指出，41%受訪的公司因為暴力衝擊而生意額下降，50%表示無影響。有16%受訪者稱，因為遊行示威而開工不足、收入下降、甚至被裁員，當中較多來自旅遊、飲食、酒店、零售和交通運輸物流等行業。<br />\n<br />\n隨機電話調查在9月23日至27日進行，訪問超過1000名<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">工聯會屬會會員</span></strong>。44%受訪者擔心未來開工不足或被裁員，另外，88%受訪者認為香港目前最重要的是恢復社會秩序。<br />\n<br />\n工聯會說，72%受訪者贊成設立緊急失業援助金，應付未來失業情況惡化的問題，建議援助金額最高每月14000元，最長派發半年，又建議僱員再培訓局的新計劃培訓津貼，由每日約154元增加到每日300元，以及增設兼職短期課程，以讓僱員自我增值。"},{"pid":"aa24730b87e0bfd293c6c0359e14e07caf1ef638","tid":1646049,"uid":307619,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-11T15:10:36.000Z","msg":"唔好意思講一講題外話<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">黃大仙龍上手足請留意！</span><br />\n街站同呢個肥仔傾過<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n發現佢好深黃值得投！<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/BhMdnqU.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FBhMdnqU.png&h=a7f5cbfa&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">更重要係：「自1994年起，工聯會林文輝已連續在龍上當選5屆區議員。」<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/XxjZhZt.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FXxjZhZt.png&h=89a4d74b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n工聯會出賣港人，以為唔洗還？"}]}